                            <b>Description</b>
                            <div class=" mt-2 bg-light p-3">
                                <p><strong>12.Write R program to do the following tests with the sample data and visualize the results graphically.&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>c) F-test&nbsp;</strong></p>                            </div>
